{
  "texts": [
    "Its judgment patterns were juxtaposed against those of both laypeople and linguists.",
    "Our findings indicate a substantial agreement between ChatGPT and humans regarding grammatical intuition, though certain distinctions were also evident.",
    "In this experiment, we presented ChatGPT with a reference sentence that had a pre-assigned acceptability rating of 100.",
    "We then asked ChatGPT to assign a rating, in multiples of this reference rating, to target sentences.",
    "This approach is a replication of the ME task from Sprouse et al. (2013), but with two key modifications."
  ]
}